			HColorCop Installation Instruction
			==================================



Required
========
QT version 4 or higher, can be freely downloaded from www.trolltech.com
or ftp.trolltech.com


Installation
============
the installation of hcolorcop is very easy, you should only enter these commands
and hcolorcop should be installed.
tar -xvzf hcolorcop-version.tar.gz
cd hcolorcop-version
make
make install


Changing installation directory
===============================
You can easaly change the installation directory during compiling by using
make DEST=directory
and
make DEST=directory install


Which files will be added
=========================
/usr/bin/hcolorcop

